<head> 
<title>Notification Email Sample Template</title> 
</head> 
<body> 
<H1>Activity Notification Sample Email</H1> 
<pre> 
Your activity has been CLOSED. 

The data in this activity record is: 

Subject: <b>$!activity.Subject</b> 

Type: <b>$!activity.Type</b> 
Priority: <b>$!activity.Priority</b> 
Mandatory: #if ($activity.isMandatory()) <b>Yes</b><br>#else <b>No</b><br>#end
Auto Generated: #if ($activity.isAutoGenerated()) <b>Yes</b><br>#else <b>No</b><br>#end
Status: <b>$!activity.Status</b> 

Description: <b>$!activity.Description</b> 

Approved: #if ($activity.isApproved()) <b>Yes</b><br>#else <b>No</b><br>#end
Recurring: #if ($activity.isRecurring()) <b>Yes</b><br>#else <b>No</b><br>#end

Claim Number: <b>$!activity.Claim.ClaimNumber</b> 

Created Time: <b>$!activity.CreateTime</b> 
Created By User: <b>$!activity.CreateUser.DisplayName</b> 

Assigned To Group: <b>$!activity.AssignedGroup.Name</b> 
Assigned To User: <b>$!activity.AssignedUser.DisplayName</b> 
Assignment Date: <b>$!activity.AssignmentDate</b> 

Previous Assigned User: <b>$!activity.PreviousUser.DisplayName</b> 
Previous Group: <b>$!activity.PreviousGroup.Name</b> 

Last Updated Time: <b>$!activity.UpdateTime</b> 
Last Updated By User: <b>$!activity.UpdateUser.DisplayName</b> 

Closed Date: <b>$!activity.CloseDate</b> 
Close By User: <b>$!activity.CloseUser.DisplayName</b> 

Target Completion Date: <b>$!activity.TargetDate</b> 
Escalated: #if ($activity.isEscalated()) <b>Yes</b><br>#else <b>No</b><br>#end 
#if ($activity.isEscalated()) 
Escalation Date: <b>$!activity.EscalationDate</b> #end 
</pre> 
</body> 
